type.description: Device Information, such as software version, OS etc.

statusProperties.name: manufacturer
statusProperties.description: Company name of the device manufacturer, e.g. Bosch.

statusProperties.name: softwareVersion
statusProperties.description: Version of the software on your device. This could be the version of your firmware, e.g. 2.4.33

statusProperties.name: osName
statusProperties.description: Name of the operating system on the device

statusProperties.name: processorArchitecture
statusProperties.description: Architecture of the processor on the device, e.g x64 or ARM.

statusProperties.name: processorManufacturer
statusProperties.description: Name of the manufacturer of the processor on the device, e.g Intel.

statusProperties.name: totalMemory
statusProperties.description: Total available memory on the device in kilobytes

statusProperties.name: totalStorage
statusProperties.description: Total available storage on the device in kilobytes
